686 A.2d 605 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION of Maryland, Petitioner, v. Michael Glenn WAGNER, Respondent. Misc. (Subtitle BV) No. 31,

Sept. Term, 1986.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Dec. 18, 1996.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the Joint Petition for Placement on Inactive Status submitted to this Court by Petitioner and Respondent, it is this 18th day of December,

ORDERED by the Court of Appeals of Maryland that the Joint Petition be, and it is hereby, granted and Michael Glenn Wagner is to be placed on Inactive Status subject to further order of this Court, and it is further

ORDERED, that the Clerk of this Court shall remove the name of Michael Glenn Wagner from the register of attorneys in this Court until further order of this Court and shall certify that fact to the Trustees of the Clients’ Security Trust Fund and the clerks of all judicial tribunals in the State in accordance with Rule BV13.
